<P>I still feel they should take it out. You can usually get a good since of whether or not you can beat them. Look at thier equipment, see how much damage they are doing in battle (monster or pvp). Use some deductive reasoning and stop relying on crutches. Too many people just run up to someone, /con them, and either attack or run away.

